with​ ​the​ ​newer​ ​versions​ ​of​ ​the​ ​technology​ ​enhancing​ ​its​ ​performance​ ​and​ ​maintenance.​ ​This​ ​application​ ​is​ ​a​ ​part​ ​of 
the​ ​BBVA​ ​banking​ ​systems​ ​simplifying​ ​its​ ​usage​ ​to​ ​the​ ​customers,​ ​allowing​ ​them​ ​to​ ​receive​ ​financial​ ​funding​ ​in

criterias.​ ​It​ ​provides​ ​information​ ​about​ ​Mortgage​ ​servicing​ ​and​ ​Loan​ ​managements​ ​and​ ​also​ ​provides​ ​online 
mortgage​ ​calculators,​ ​enquiry​ ​forms​ ​and​ ​other​ ​credit​ ​services​ ​to​ ​the​ ​customers,​ ​ensure​ ​them​ ​with​ ​higher​ ​standards 
of​ ​accountability​ ​and​ ​transparency​ ​in​ ​their​ ​services.
